{"tid":2374691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"體藝生移民英國前，凌晨4點撐艇1.5小時返校留城門河回憶","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T13:11:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":150,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9ea705264ba8ce8dfcc8481354dcd3472ce79b","tid":2374691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IfAvlRvY9VMVOTCIOnMMMQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NC4wNjI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/SohDW8rtMvxy3QDR7Bk4mg--~B/aD01OTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/8db38bc67ed6a9ddd212bdceb612db99\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIfAvlRvY9VMVOTCIOnMMMQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NC4wNjI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSohDW8rtMvxy3QDR7Bk4mg--~B%2FaD01OTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F8db38bc67ed6a9ddd212bdceb612db99&h=decdfdb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離開香港前，讓青春無悔！一名體藝生在移民英國前，與同學們做了一件十分熱血的事，凌晨4點起身，撐足1.5小時艇回校上學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gofw7BK33dtM2O1zcLQb4g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OS4zNzU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/jpCk7RM31tfddX4d0fmSPA--~B/aD02MTg7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/d229e2c9c18f19d2c8e18d1cb445d878\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fgofw7BK33dtM2O1zcLQb4g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OS4zNzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjpCk7RM31tfddX4d0fmSPA--~B%2FaD02MTg7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2Fd229e2c9c18f19d2c8e18d1cb445d878&h=1132cf43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「年青人，係乜驅使你凌晨4點起身，有巴士唔搭，要出海撐個半鐘頭艇返學呀？」3名現正就讀賽馬會體藝中學的男學生，去年10月想出了一個瘋狂的想法，就是撐艇上學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u9wZVo9qErJZc96.6V9nCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyOS42ODc1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/qZs8XAENOb7SJkH8h0zHvw--~B/aD01NjU7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/5aa125cb2ef321ec73a15b0e1070bc22\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fu9wZVo9qErJZc96.6V9nCw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyOS42ODc1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqZs8XAENOb7SJkH8h0zHvw--~B%2FaD01NjU7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F5aa125cb2ef321ec73a15b0e1070bc22&h=9b14ebf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們非常之認真，有預先規劃路線，並練習部份路段，更將過程拍成YouTube短片Vlog。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GGwpTZ5cq2GOjXb0JAFIWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMy4xMjU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/3csY3PXHVsKFYZJrussCgA--~B/aD01NTg7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/bd1594e53ba5c5f253a798aac420b230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGGwpTZ5cq2GOjXb0JAFIWw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMy4xMjU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3csY3PXHVsKFYZJrussCgA--~B%2FaD01NTg7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2Fbd1594e53ba5c5f253a798aac420b230&h=120c9357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片中主角Sun就是搞手，他與兩名同學天未光就由烏溪沙出發，沿著城門河，一直撐到火炭的體藝中學，撐艇全程1.5小時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VkzwvNn5x8DTXN9aQTsqDg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwMi44MTI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/KvZZSQgwcjpncQSu7Gyk1w--~B/aD02NDM7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/49d499b25d75d2560b26cb4b7b5d743a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVkzwvNn5x8DTXN9aQTsqDg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwMi44MTI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKvZZSQgwcjpncQSu7Gyk1w--~B%2FaD02NDM7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F49d499b25d75d2560b26cb4b7b5d743a&h=02fdfd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n期間Sun的拍檔偷懶，令Sun獨力支撐前進動力，撐到滿頭海水，但他亦堅持完成，盡展體藝生的驚人體力與毅力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/f0WzbxX8j1NufWM2C25uoQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyNC4wNjI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/hhhhfI4HMKdCQWolyP6Zdw--~B/aD01NTk7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/2c6311c3bc3282fffa63fca351a2b352\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Ff0WzbxX8j1NufWM2C25uoQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyNC4wNjI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhhhhfI4HMKdCQWolyP6Zdw--~B%2FaD01NTk7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F2c6311c3bc3282fffa63fca351a2b352&h=42682d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n短片一出，馬上紅爆網絡，不少體藝校友都大讚Sun和同學們青春熱血，拍片技巧很好。他們出動Gopro與航拍，片段亦剪接得很順暢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ltf9g5FgmNLTWo0TfWSL3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MS41NjI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/h.2zGsKtMdDdoa0f1FPElQ--~B/aD01OTk7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/72ab54e834aee0e6ecd6f7142a721d4e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fltf9g5FgmNLTWo0TfWSL3Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MS41NjI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fh.2zGsKtMdDdoa0f1FPElQ--~B%2FaD01OTk7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F72ab54e834aee0e6ecd6f7142a721d4e&h=31c3fbde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而網民亦非常欣賞三名男生的純真和努力，特別是片末加插他們到達火炭後吃早餐和步行上學的過程，勾起許多人昔日上學的青春回憶，又大讚幾名男生十分可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k3hJIGQ.nihDj02HO8gibg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1Ni44NzU-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Q0ntFnqeeyzUb0otAXkmgw--~B/aD01OTQ7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/3a01d3f2bef02512dcfab5ce3ca99469\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fk3hJIGQ.nihDj02HO8gibg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1Ni44NzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQ0ntFnqeeyzUb0otAXkmgw--~B%2FaD01OTQ7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F3a01d3f2bef02512dcfab5ce3ca99469&h=4f687b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而近年香港爆發移民潮，主角Sun亦在去年12月發表Vlog，表示自己身處英國曼徹斯特的生活，包括去中式超市、在曼徹斯特過聖誕，但他不是去旅行，而是與家人一起離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K5np7JT5adTkOC_DTAHvtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUxNi41NjI1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/XnLwfV5vqlEQxvKy.ibj9Q--~B/aD01NTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/2e4625dc2a1efe199955feb587f92431\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FK5np7JT5adTkOC_DTAHvtw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUxNi41NjI1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXnLwfV5vqlEQxvKy.ibj9Q--~B%2FaD01NTE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F2e4625dc2a1efe199955feb587f92431&h=5618f98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他表示「係去移民呀，Yeah！」。Sun因忙著收拾物品，故此近期片量減少，直到近日發佈撐艇Vlog就紅爆網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JRXQZ9I2tOse3jW6dbzZXA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1OS42ODc1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/7vdgFpMgzwnxfqY4CXfU3w--~B/aD01OTc7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/642f9062b83f5e6042853766b026fc40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJRXQZ9I2tOse3jW6dbzZXA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1OS42ODc1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7vdgFpMgzwnxfqY4CXfU3w--~B%2FaD01OTc7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F642f9062b83f5e6042853766b026fc40&h=324b2467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然Sun要離開香港，到英國定居，但他與同學們在城門河留下的青春印記，相信足以一生難忘，也是他與好友的美好回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/s2kjnLHPSVucgJy5gtgFfA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNy4xODc1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/2Aa6vFh6PTGyyG1oYR1w3w--~B/aD01NDE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/86fa0e2db84812ecfbcfdf43dcffc49f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs2kjnLHPSVucgJy5gtgFfA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNy4xODc1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2Aa6vFh6PTGyyG1oYR1w3w--~B%2FaD01NDE7dz0xMDI0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F86fa0e2db84812ecfbcfdf43dcffc49f&h=7f23e3eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正如他講「我覺得中學生涯一定要玩吓呢啲，咁先有個回憶喺到。」"},{"pid":"1b0d3ba12cbbcbd82cd40d2557f1477d67e10711","tid":2374691,"uid":199893,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"行動力高到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多人諗完得個講字<br />\nRespect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59262a3e4cd7f125da596e56bda883b80fabf8df","tid":2374691,"uid":328026,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qX5XYuTBzy4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqX5XYuTBzy4&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=8d0dd3ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht